West of Memphis;;87;;95;;R;;Filmmaker Amy Berg tells the story of the fight to stop the state of Arkansas from executing an innocent man. Beginning with an examination into the police investigation into the 1993 murders of three boys in West Memphis, Arkansas, Berg brings to light new evidence surrounding the arrest and conviction of Damien Echols, Jason Baldwin and Jessie Misskelley. All three were teens at the time and lost 18 years of their lives after being wrongly convicted and imprisoned.;;Documentary,Crime,Drama;;Amy Berg;;2012;;Michael Baden,Jason Baldwin,John Mark Byers,Lorri Davis,Johnny Depp,Julie Ann Doan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/west_of_memphis